Frank the people are real, at least where Ryan, Lorraine and Chip are concerned. Hacks they may be but none the less real. Lorraine and Ed Warren are the ones who still claim Amityville even though no one before or after the Lutz&#39;s claimed any activity. Ryan is just another Johnny come lately! Chip, well i like Chip and can&#39;t believe he is associating himself with them. I don&#39;t know the other investigators. Unfortunately, their group and show concentrate on the spooky, scary, evil, where out to steal your soul bullshit. 

I laugh throughout the entire show and my favorite phrase is, OMG I can&#39;t believe they told them that! Like you said, its entertainment and no one I know takes it seriously. Not even my kids (boys 5 and 8).

Frank R.

